---
description: Remove origin traces and preserve professional brand tone
alwaysApply: true
---

# No Provenance Traces

- Do not include automation-signature language in user-facing copy or deliverables.
- Do not expose internal prompting/process text in UI content.
- Avoid generic filler copy that feels machine-generated.

# Brand Tone

- Keep tone professional, specific, and context-aware.
- Prefer confident, concise language over verbose explanations.
- Match the user's preferred language and style.
